OL,6,F's co-founder has been given a
OL,7,Fsuspended sentence after plotting with
OL,8,Fothers to fly drones near .
OL,10,FRoger Hallam and other eco-activists,
OL,11,Fwanted to close the airport until the
OL,12,FGovernment reversed plans for a third
OL,13,Frunway.
OL,15,FThey wanted backing for the protest,
OL,16,Flaunched under the name Heathrow
OL,17,FPause, to go viral and shut down the
OL,18,Fairport while also triggering arrests
OL,19,Fand lots of publicity, London's
OL,20,FIsleworth Crown Court was told during
OL,21,Fthe trial.
