OL,3,CExtinction Rebellion co-founder spared
OL,4,Cjail over conspiracy to close Heathrow
OL,6,FHallam and co-defendant Larch Maxey
OL,7,Fsaid in their defence they had no
OL,8,Fintent to cause a public nuisance or
OL,9,Fto close Heathrow, it was "merely a
OL,10,Fpublicity exercise," which was
OL,11,Frejected by the jury, James Curtis KC,
OL,12,Fprosecuting, said.
OL,14,FA number of arrests were made during
OL,15,Fthe protest in September 2019, but
OL,16,Finstead of hundreds of people
OL,17,Fattending to fly drones, the "movement
OL,18,Fdied where it was," Mr Curtis said.
