OL,3,CExtinction Rebellion co-founder spared
OL,4,Cjail over conspiracy to close Heathrow
OL,6,FHallam, 57, of Wandsworth, south
OL,7,FLondon, and Maxey, 51, of no fixed
OL,8,Fabode, were found guilty of conspiracy
OL,9,Fto cause a public nuisance on 15
OL,10,FDecember 2023 after a four-week trial.
OL,12,FMichael Lynch-White, 33, of ,
OL,13,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to the same
OL,14,Fcharge.
OL,16,FValerie Milner-Brown, 71, of
OL,17,FIslington, north London, was found not
OL,18,Fguilty of conspiracy to cause a public
OL,19,Fnuisance.
