OL,3,CExtinction Rebellion co-founder spared
OL,4,Cjail over conspiracy to close Heathrow
OL,6,FThe court heard Hallam, Maxey and
OL,7,FLynch-White conspired with others on
OL,8,For before 14 September 2019 to close
OL,9,Fthe transport hub to air traffic by
OL,10,Fthe "unlawful flying" of drones within
OL,11,FHeathrow's flight restriction zone.
OL,13,FMr Curtis said the intention was "not
OL,14,Fto close it for a day, but some
OL,15,Fdocuments say a week, two weeks" and
OL,16,Fhe said there are documents which show
OL,17,Fthe intention was to close Heathrow
OL,18,F"indefinitely until the Government
OL,19,Fwould agree publicly to reverse a
OL,20,Fnational policy permitting the third
OL,21,Frunway extension at Heathrow."
