OL,3,CExtinction Rebellion co-founder spared
OL,4,Cjail over conspiracy to close Heathrow
OL,6,FThere was no intention to cause any
OL,7,Fcrash or to harm or endanger lives of
OL,8,Findividuals, but with the "intention
OL,9,Fof causing inevitable chaos to the
OL,10,Fpublic," Mr Curtis said.
OL,12,FMr Curtis said documents show the
OL,13,Fintention was to cause "massive
OL,14,Fdisruption to the public, to flights
OL,15,Fin and out of this country."
OL,17,FHeathrow Airport and the police had to
OL,18,Fgo to "inordinate lengths to prepare
OL,19,Ffor the worst," Mr Curtis said.
