OL,3,CExtinction Rebellion co-founder spared
OL,4,Cjail over conspiracy to close Heathrow
OL,6,FCourt documents showed how policing
OL,7,Fcost to the public was in excess of #1
OL,8,Fmillion, and 1,600 officer shifts had
OL,9,Fto be moved.
OL,11,FHallam said the "public nuisance was
OL,12,Finsignificant to non-existent in my
OL,13,Fcase" and there was "no evidence" he
OL,14,Fplayed a leadership role in this
OL,15,Foffence.
OL,17,FHe added: "The public nuisance was
OL,18,Fsimply to create publicity for the
OL,19,Fcriminality of creating a third
OL,20,Frunway."
