OL,3,CExtinction Rebellion co-founder spared
OL,4,Cjail over conspiracy to close Heathrow
OL,6,FHallam and Maxey were each sentenced
OL,7,Fto two years in prison, suspended for
OL,8,F18 months.
OL,10,FLynch-White was handed 17 months,
OL,11,Fsuspended for 18 months.
OL,13,FHallam was told to complete 200 hours
OL,14,Fof unpaid work, Maxey has to complete
OL,15,F300 hours and Lynch-White will have to
OL,16,Fcomplete 262 hours. All three
OL,17,Fdefendants will have to complete 10
OL,18,Frehabilitation activity requirement
OL,19,Fdays.
